</table>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="900">7. Viewing the activity index</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>Activity index</strong> area in the <strong>Customers » Edit customers »</strong> menu displays e.g. how long the person has been your customer and when he or she has been logged into your online store for the last time. This data will be automatically updated and cannot be changed. Table 5 explains the customer’s activity index.</p>
</div>
