<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Account type</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Account via which the customer has registered. Either <strong>regular account</strong> or <strong>guest account</strong>. Regular account means that the customer has newly registered in your online store. Guest account means that the customer has ordered as a guest without registering in your online store.</p>
